lead_paragraph: Gordon Hayward had 27 points and 12 rebounds, Rodney Hood added 19 points and the Utah Jazz beat the Chicago Bulls 105-96 in overtime on Monday night.

headline.print_headline: Hayward Has 27 Points, 12 Rebounds as Jazz Beat Bulls in OT
